data.text: @_Trapitalism @bayani13 Yup. I also loved how early 00s Rock and DC put their people on who were also hella brilliant and hilarious, ie Wanda Sykes and Charlie Murphy.

@bayani13 @kchen510 DEF early 00s Rock, but I like/love both versions of DC. I hella appreciate how he grapples with tough shit right in front of everyone & let's ppl have whatever feels they wanna have while making it funny & having solid points--bruh still a genius (imo)

@kchen510 @bayani13 Felt like most recent Chappelle's were actually pretty well done, funny, & in certain moments hella poignant & deep--but that's bc he understands who he is/context/reads his audiences hella well & he hella refines his material--Rock sounded outta touch & irrelevant
@bayani13 @_Trapitalism Deeeeaaam, blud, very true 😣 Come on, Rock, chalk this one up and bounce back.
